                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <article class="post ">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">EMPRESA INDIVIDUAL</h3><h4>A Empresa Individual de Responsabilidade Limitada, ou Empresa Individual Ltda é um tipo de sociedade que consiste em que uma pessoa apenas constitua uma situação jurídica. Descubra tudo sobre empresa individual Ltda aqui!</h4>
                            <ul class="info">
                                <li>
                                    <div class="text date">segunda-feira, 22 de fevereiro de 2016</div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <i class="entyp-pencil-1"></i>
                                    <div class="text">Publicado por CONDUX</div>
                                </li>
                                
                                <li>
                                    <a href="/noticias/?cat=Empresarial">
                                        <i class="entyp-list-1"></i>
                                        <div class="text">Empresarial</div>
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                
                            </ul>
                            
                            <figure>
                                <img src="https://condux.com.br/site/imgnews/140c.jpg" alt="EMPRESA INDIVIDUAL"/>
                                
                            </figure>
                            
                            <div class="content">
                            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 0.69cm;">A responsabilidade da pessoa jur&iacute;dica e pessoa titular do empreendimento n&atilde;o se confunde ou se relaciona, essa decis&atilde;o provem da Lei da Empresa Individual, n&ordm; 12.441, de 2011, antes da referida lei era necess&aacute;rio a exist&ecirc;ncia de, pelo menos, dois s&oacute;cios, o que muitas vezes gerava fraudes.</span></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 0.69cm;">Para melhor conceitua&ccedil;&atilde;o da Empresa Individual consideraremos algumas defini&ccedil;&otilde;es:</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A empresa Individual representa um novo ente jur&iacute;dico.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O patrim&ocirc;nio da empresa individual responde pelas d&iacute;vidas que a empresa contrair e n&atilde;o se confunde com o patrim&ocirc;nio da pessoa natural que caracteriza o empres&aacute;rio ou empres&aacute;rio individual.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O empres&aacute;rio da empresa individual pode ser representado em tr&ecirc;s categorias:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(32, 32, 32);"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Empresario Individual, Empreendedor Individual ou Microempreendedor Individual &ndash;&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></span><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">representa a pessoa f&iacute;sica que tem responsabilidade pessoal e ilimitada quanto&nbsp;</font></font><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">&agrave;s</font></font><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es da empresa</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(32, 32, 32);"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Sociedade Empres&aacute;ria &ndash;&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></span><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">trata da pluralidade de titulares, considerando cada esp&eacute;cie de responsabilidade, seja sociedade an&ocirc;nima, sociedade em comandita simples e outros.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(32, 32, 32);"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Empresa Individual de Responsabilidade Limitada &ndash;&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></span><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">representa uma sociedade de natureza jur&iacute;dica com patrim&ocirc;nio constitu&iacute;do e responsabilidade limitada e obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es devidas &agrave;s opera&ccedil;&otilde;es.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Objetivos da Lei de Empresa Individual</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A lei para Empresa Individual tem o objetivo de estimular a formaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de empresas que funcionam de forma informal no mercado e ainda brechas que possa haver na forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de empresa individual como:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Sociedades simuladas compostas por s&oacute;cios que emprestam o nome para que haja a pluralidade de titulares.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A lei busca a extin&ccedil;&atilde;o de sociedade depois dos 180 dias que s&atilde;o concedidos legalmente.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A firma poder&aacute; utilizar nome fantasia desde que acompanhada da sigla EIRELI.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A responsabilidade pelas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es da empresa decorre do patrim&ocirc;nio que &eacute; constitu&iacute;do pela pessoa jur&iacute;dica.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">N&atilde;o podem integrar o capital social os recursos como imagem, o nome, a voz e outros.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Forma&ccedil;&atilde;o do Capital</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O capital social da empresa &eacute; constitu&iacute;do por uma &uacute;nica pessoa responsabilidade pela integraliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do capital.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O capital social ser&aacute; de 100 vezes o valor do sal&aacute;rio-m&iacute;nimo vigente no pa&iacute;s e n&atilde;o podendo ser inferior a este valor.</font></font></span></span></p>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Formaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da Empresa</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A empresa individual ser&aacute; acompanhada da sigla EIRELI. Outra peculiaridade da empresa &eacute; que a pessoa natural conforme a lei poder&aacute; ser titular de apenas uma EIRELI.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A&nbsp;</font></font><em style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal;">empresa individual&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></em><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">pode tamb&eacute;m surgir da concentra&ccedil;&atilde;o de quotas em um &uacute;nico s&oacute;cio sem considerar a motiva&ccedil;&atilde;o para a concentra&ccedil;&atilde;o.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Quanto as atividades a legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o prev&ecirc; que a EIRELI pode constituir qualquer natureza de atividade para presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Sendo obrigat&oacute;ria a remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o de direitos autorais, de &aacute;udio, visual, imagem e marca que estejam vinculados a realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o das atividades.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Diversas d&uacute;vidas surgem quando uma empresa individual decide abrir as portas. Uma das principais &eacute; como abrir empresa individual, portanto vamos considerar alguns fatores para a abertura de empresas:</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A empresa individual paga mais impostos? Isso n&atilde;o &eacute; verdadeiro, pois as empresas individuais possuem as mesmas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es que as sociedades e algumas empresas individuais podem optar pelo Simples, desde que a natureza n&atilde;o seja impeditiva.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(32, 32, 32);"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Como Registro Minha Empresa &ndash;&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></span><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">na abertura de empresa individual devem ser consideradas diversas caracter&iacute;sticas:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O titular possui responsabilidade ilimitada com seu patrim&ocirc;nio pessoal.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Principio da Entidade &ndash; o princ&iacute;pio da entidade n&atilde;o &eacute; obedecido, pois as obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es quanto ao patrim&ocirc;nio do titular confunde-se com o da firma individual.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Quando h&aacute; morte do titular, os bens da firma individual n&atilde;o s&atilde;o transferidos para outra pessoa.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Uma&nbsp;</font></font><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(32, 32, 32);"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">empresa individual&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></span><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">n&atilde;o &eacute; transformada em sociedade.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O nome social na empresa deve conter o nome do titular e a sigla EIRELI.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Um titular pode possuir apenas uma empresa de responsabilidade individual.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Para abrir a&nbsp;</font></font><em style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal;">empresa individual&nbsp;</span></font></font></font></em><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">o empres&aacute;rio dever&aacute; se inscrever no Registro P&uacute;blico de Empresas Mercantis.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o deve ser realizada com requerimento que contenha: Nome, nacionalidade, o domic&iacute;lio, estado civil, regime de bens, capital, objeto, sede da empresa.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O empres&aacute;rio que tenha como atividade principal a atividade rural deve requerer registro p&uacute;blico de empresas mercantis.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">No mais, s&atilde;o consideradas empresas individuais:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A Firma individual.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">As empresas de pessoas f&iacute;sicas que exploram atividades profissionais com fins lucrativos.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A empresa individual n&atilde;o se aplica a profiss&otilde;es como:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">M&eacute;dico;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Engenheiro;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Advogado;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Professor;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Dentista;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Escultor;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Pintor.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">E ainda profiss&otilde;es para servi&ccedil;os n&atilde;o comerciais como:</font></font></span></span></p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;">
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Representantes;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Agentes sem v&iacute;nculo empregat&iacute;cio;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Corretores;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Leiloeiros;</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="box-sizing: border-box;">
    <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Despachantes e outros.</font></font></span></span></p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Ou explora&ccedil;&atilde;o individual de atividades apenas de labor como: arquitetura, topografia, alvenaria e outros.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">E explora&ccedil;&atilde;o de atividades art&iacute;sticas, culturais e educa&ccedil;&atilde;o pelo principal autor.</font></font></span></span></p>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Responsabilidade do Empres&aacute;rio</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Sempre que um empres&aacute;rio pretende abrir um determinado tipo de sociedade empresarial deve se dedicar a conhecer a legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o e todas as possibilidades envolvidas na legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o para a Empresa Individual.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Na Empresa de Responsabilidade Individual de Responsabilidade Limitada o empres&aacute;rio possui diversas responsabilidades, entre elas est&atilde;o:</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Os s&oacute;cios-gerentes respondem de forma solid&aacute;ria quando existe excesso de mandato ou atos praticados na viola&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato ou lei que rege a EIRELI. Sem preju&iacute;zo da responsabilidade criminal quando h&aacute; abuso de firma social, havendo perdas e danos.</font></font></span></span></p>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Caracter&iacute;stica da Empresa</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">As caracter&iacute;sticas da empresa est&atilde;o relacionadas a forma&ccedil;&atilde;o de capital, a titularidade de sociedade empres&aacute;ria. Entre uma das principais caracter&iacute;sticas da empresa individual est&atilde;o:</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O fato de que quando a firma &eacute; individual h&aacute; somente um s&oacute;cio empres&aacute;rio e, portanto, n&atilde;o existe distin&ccedil;&atilde;o entre o patrim&ocirc;nio da empresa e o patrim&ocirc;nio do s&oacute;cio. Portanto, os bens do s&oacute;cio e do propriet&aacute;rio podem ser penhorados assim que houver a necessidade de pagamentos de d&iacute;vidas por motivo de fal&ecirc;ncia.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;">Com isso, a participa&ccedil;&atilde;o societ&aacute;ria concede aos s&oacute;cios e empres&aacute;rios a</font></font>&nbsp;<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;">responsabilidade de pagamentos das d&iacute;vidas e obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es contra&iacute;das.</font></font></font></font></font></span></span></p>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal;">Vantagens e Desvantagens</span></u></font></font></font></span></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A lei que rege a Empresa representa um avan&ccedil;o do mundo jur&iacute;dico comercial, mas tamb&eacute;m imp&otilde;e diversas d&uacute;vidas, sobretudo em empreendedores novos no ramo das empresas individuais.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Uma das d&uacute;vidas &eacute; quanto &agrave;s vantagens e desvantagens de optar por uma empresa individual, ent&atilde;o vejamos:</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Como vantagem, temos que a empresa individual representa a possibilidade de abrir uma empresa individual com somente uma pessoa. A empresa ser&aacute; exercida de forma singular e s&oacute; comprometer&aacute; o patrim&ocirc;nio pessoal do empres&aacute;rio, caso exista determina&ccedil;&atilde;o legal.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">N&atilde;o h&aacute; necessidade de um s&oacute;cio fict&iacute;cio o que torna a empresa mais transparente, com isso, seu patrim&ocirc;nio ser&aacute; protegido, salvo riscos empresariais.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Em outra legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o existia a possibilidade de pessoa jur&iacute;dica atuando de forma individual, o que ocorria &eacute; que este empres&aacute;rio exercia o com&eacute;rcio de forma individual sem a denomina&ccedil;&atilde;o de empres&aacute;rio.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Outra vantagem &eacute; quanto a formalidade advinda da EIRELI aumentando o n&uacute;mero de empresas individuais que atuam no mercado de forma legalizada.</font></font></span></span></p>
<h2 class="western" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.01cm; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); margin-top: 0.79cm; margin-bottom: 0.53cm; font-size: 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#000000" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20pt;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;">Desvantagens da EIRELI</u></font></font></font></span></span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">Entre os desafios principais enfrentados pelas EIRELI s&atilde;o:</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">A pessoa jur&iacute;dica pode figurar apenas uma empresa da categoria empresa individual, sendo que mesmo n&atilde;o sendo uma desvantagem representa uma limita&ccedil;&atilde;o para este empres&aacute;rio.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.69cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 0.69cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#222222" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">O capital inicial &eacute; outro ponto limitador, pois &eacute; necess&aacute;rio um investimento inicial de 100 sal&aacute;rios-m&iacute;nimos vigentes no pa&iacute;s.</font></font></span></span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; color: rgb(163, 163, 163); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 16px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;Fonte: Novo Neg&oacute;cio</span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
                            </div>
                            
                        </article>
                        
                        
                    </div>
